ZH: 我缺乏经验，不知道该怎么处理这个问题。
EN: I lack experience and don't know how to handle this problem.

ZH: 缺乏运动会导致身体变得虚弱。
EN: Lack of exercise can result in a weak body.

ZH: 学生晚上睡眠不足，缺乏精力上课。
EN: Students who have insufficient sleep at night lack energy in class.

