EN: Lack of teamwork spirit can affect work efficiency.

ZH: 这个地区缺乏可靠的公共交通系统。
EN: This area lacks a reliable public transportation system.

ZH: 缺乏耐心的人通常不能从长远的角度考虑问题。
EN: People who lack patience usually cannot consider things from a long-term perspective.

ZH: 缺乏沟通导致了许多不必要的误解。
EN: Lack of communication has caused many unnecessary misunderstandings.

ZH: 社会上普遍缺乏对残疾人的关注和支持。
EN: There is a general lack of attention and support for disabled people in society.

ZH: 她缺乏自信，总是怀疑自己的能力。
EN: She lacks confidence and always doubts her abilities.

ZH: 缺乏正确的教育，孩子们无法获得良好的启蒙。
EN: Without proper education, children cannot receive a good start in life.

ZH: 这个项目缺乏足够的资金来完成。
EN: This project lacks sufficient funds to be completed.

ZH: 缺乏决心和毅力会使人无法坚持自己的目标。
EN: Lack of determination and perseverance can prevent someone from achieving their goals.

